iphlog, art, intimde diary or anything else. In my opinion,	/	tilde.team	70
ithe author of baud.baby explains it perfectly in this post.	/	tilde.team	70
iAs he says, for older people it may be nostalgia for old	/	tilde.team	70
itechnologies, others like the simplicity of the protocol and	/	tilde.team	70
ifile format.	/	tilde.team	70
